---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Projects" lang="en">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      
<div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-cyan-500/20 mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M9.352 4C4.456 7.456 1 13.12 1 19.36c0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.36 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.208-5.472-5.088-5.472-.576 0-1.344.096-1.536.192.48-3.264 3.552-7.104 6.624-9.024L9.352 4zm16.512 0c-4.896 3.456-8.352 9.12-8.352 15.36 0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.264 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.304-5.472-5.184-5.472-.576 0-1.248.096-1.44.192.48-3.264 3.456-7.104 6.528-9.024L25.864 4z" />
              </svg>
              <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 italic mb-6">
                "The training opened my eyes and helped me understand the possibilities that artificial intelligence offers."
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-cyan-900 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-400 font-bold border border-cyan-500/30">
                  WP
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-white font-bold">Wiktoria Papała</div>
                  <div class="text-cyan-400 text-sm">Owner, Papaja Tatuaże</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transition-all hover:border-cyan-500/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(6,182,212,0.15)]">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-0">
          
          <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 border-b lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r border-slate-700">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-400/10 rounded-full">AI Marketing</span>
              <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium">Poznań, 2025</span>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">AI in Creative Marketing</h2>
            <h3 class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-6 font-medium">Client: <span class="text-white">Papaja Tatuaże</span></h3>
            
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              In collaboration with a creative tattoo studio, we demonstrated how Artificial Intelligence tools can drastically support marketing efforts and expand social media reach.
            </p>

            <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-4">Scope of Implementation & Training:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg width="24" height="24" class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0 text-cyan-400 mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-slate-300">AI tools for generating video scripts for TikTok and Instagram Reels.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg width="24" height="24" class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0 text-cyan-400 mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-slate-300">Intelligent editors for video and audio post-production.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg width="24" height="24" class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0 text-cyan-400 mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-slate-300">Solutions assisting in writing promotional content and engaging post descriptions.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 bg-slate-800/80 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Operational Impact</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
              Thanks to our training, the Papaja Tatuaże studio unlocked entirely new capabilities in creating engaging content. The time required for promotional material production was optimized, directly resulting in increased reach and client interaction.
            </p>

            <div class="relative bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50">
              <svg class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-8 h-8 text-cyan-500/20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M9.352 4C4.456 7.456 1 13.12 1 19.36c0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.36 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.208-5.472-5.088-5.472-.576 0-1.344.096-1.536.192.48-3.264 3.552-7.104 6.624-9.024L9.352 4zm16.512 0c-4.896 3.456-8.352 9.12-8.352 15.36 0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.264 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.304-5.472-5.184-5.472-.576 0-1.248.096-1.44.192.48-3.264 3.456-7.104 6.528-9.024L25.864 4z" />
              </svg>
              <p class="relative text-lg text-slate-300 italic mb-6 z-10 pl-8">
                "The training opened my eyes and helped me understand the possibilities that artificial intelligence offers."
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pl-8">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-cyan-900 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-400 font-bold border border-cyan-500/30">
                  WP
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-white font-bold">Wiktoria Papała</div>
                  <div class="text-cyan-400 text-sm">Owner, Papaja Tatuaże</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
